  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Dear Diary.

    

    Today was a good day. I put on two hats, teleported
    five times, and watched a video about Unity on the TV on repeat for 3 hours.

    

    Oh
    almost forgot  also bounced a ball on my tennis racket seven times in a row,
    which is a new personal best

    

    I can''t wait to see what tomorrow brings.

    

    With
    love,

    

    - Carl'
